            "language": "zh-CN"
        },
        {
            "id": "20250409A09VZ6",
            "title": "支付宝再度更新，这功能有点刺激啊",
            "description": "<div class=\"rich_media_content\"><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><img class=\"wxw-img rich_pages\" data-imgfileid=\"604119837\" data-ratio=\"0.9393939393939394\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OrnqJkIXZE_PThc_oT33WK-lbesjejrNizIuZgPdlgmJcAA/641\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"33\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OrnqJkIXZE_PThc_oT33WK-lbesjejrNizIuZgPdlgmJcAA/641\"/>众所周知。</section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><br/></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\">自打去年支付宝推出「碰一下」这个功能以来，官方就一直在不断扩充它的使用场景。<br/></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><br/></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\">起初的时候，它要解决的问题，是更方便快捷的「碰一下支付」。</section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><br/></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OBIHDj0alW2p8Rh_iEwcj9mTePdz_1kChAJIN842nC2-QAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OBIHDj0alW2p8Rh_iEwcj9mTePdz_1kChAJIN842nC2-QAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 4px 4px 0.5em 0px;transition:none;width:100%;height:100%\"/></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><br/></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\">后来呢，随着这个功能逐渐铺开后。</section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><br/></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><img class=\"wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"604119841\" data-ratio=\"0.7073170731707317\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OqVQNJTH3VqsikeTMHoQiVAfVtM6jhsZp-AxLskdz7NWMAA/641\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"41\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OqVQNJTH3VqsikeTMHoQiVAfVtM6jhsZp-AxLskdz7NWMAA/641\"/>支付宝又陆续搞出了「碰一下点餐」、<span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\">网吧「碰一下一键</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\">上机</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\">」、饿了么骑手「碰一下开门」<span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\">等多项新型的碰一下体验。</span></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><br/></section><p style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;text-align:center;width:auto\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OGS41CmhHa1HHxIRr0SumlJubn0vKW-jhX1x2IxTK0QaoAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OGS41CmhHa1HHxIRr0SumlJubn0vKW-jhX1x2IxTK0QaoAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 4px 4px 0.5em 0px;transition:none;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em\"><img class=\"wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"604119848\" data-ratio=\"0.7906976744186046\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/O674t7rFsNEYUiw49fL9KtVMIBqfXrhU85q3Q1ojY-kk8AA/641\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"43\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/O674t7rFsNEYUiw49fL9KtVMIBqfXrhU85q3Q1ojY-kk8AA/641\"/>眼看着这些功能不断受到网友好评。</span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em\">今天支付宝又再度出手，新增了一个</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em\">「<span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\">碰一下</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\">进小区</span>」的功能。</span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em\">根据官方发布的消息，支付宝目前已经和绿城服务展开合作。</span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em\">在支持该服务的小区中，现在只需解锁手机并碰一下门禁设备，首次授权验证后即可完成快速开门。</span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><br/></section><p style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;text-align:center;width:auto\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OathEcySBpnZbxip6QDdnl0GNNAvu29e3crQNG0oN5yX8AA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OathEcySBpnZbxip6QDdnl0GNNAvu29e3crQNG0oN5yX8AA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 4px 4px 0.5em 0px;transition:none;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><br/></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><img class=\"wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"604119844\" data-ratio=\"0.8333333333333334\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OaZs_XuYjrNWyNNbW7dTQdIHC-RVXbuuunMgmWfCjbNkAAA/641\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"36\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OaZs_XuYjrNWyNNbW7dTQdIHC-RVXbuuunMgmWfCjbNkAAA/641\"/>除了业主之外。</section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><br/></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\">针对到访的访客，全新的<span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\">「</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\">碰一下服务</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\">」也可以实现一碰外呼开门。</span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\">对于物业的工作人员来说，现在则是可以通过「碰一下」，来进行工作信息的录入。</span><br/></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\"><img class=\"wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"604119845\" data-ratio=\"0.6829268292682927\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OhFMSEFNUrrbquoTDHKWNqOS3swQsSuojcKRgnWvBOuyIAA/641\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"41\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OhFMSEFNUrrbquoTDHKWNqOS3swQsSuojcKRgnWvBOuyIAA/641\"/>相当于，一箭三雕。<br/></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;text-align:center;width:auto\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/O5NbJHDylm56bD2OZu1CrwPCE-qB7FSezn_N2bgA4g30QAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/O5NbJHDylm56bD2OZu1CrwPCE-qB7FSezn_N2bgA4g30QAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 4px 4px 0.5em 0px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;text-align:center;width:auto\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;text-align:justify;width:auto\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\"><img class=\"wxw-img rich_pages\" data-imgfileid=\"604119847\" data-ratio=\"0.9032258064516129\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OnCsReInM5PZp56to7-1V-6HAMdam_-0c6pYIXejWy3EMAA/641\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"31\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OnCsReInM5PZp56to7-1V-6HAMdam_-0c6pYIXejWy3EMAA/641\"/>虽说对于大部分安卓用户来说。<br/></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;text-align:justify;width:auto\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;text-align:justify;width:auto\">门禁卡并非什么新鲜的功能。<br/></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;text-align:justify;width:auto\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;text-align:justify;width:auto\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1.5px\">但如果是 iPhone 用户的话，这功能应该算得上「史诗级更新」吧？</span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span></span></section><section style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><br/></section><p style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;width:auto\"><span style=\"outline:0px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(214, 214, 214);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1.7px;outline:0px;text-align:left\">图片来自网络</span></span></p><p style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-left:0.5em;margin-right:0.5em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;text-align:left;width:auto\"><br/></p><p style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;text-align:right;width:auto\"><span style=\"color:rgb(64, 118, 0)\"><strong>iPhone 终于能用门禁卡了吗...</strong></span></p><p style=\"font-size:15px;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0em;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;text-align:right;width:auto\"><span style=\"color:rgb(64, 118, 0)\"><strong>↘↘↘</strong></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify\"></span></p></div>",
